snippet: Drew Stafford scored twice, and Connor Hellebuyck stopped 32 shots to lead the Winnipeg Jets to a 6-1 home victory over the Toronto Maple Leafs.
abstract: Winnipeg Jets defeat Toronto Maple Leafs, 6-1.
lead_paragraph: Drew Stafford scored twice, and Connor Hellebuyck stopped 32 shots to lead the Winnipeg Jets to a 6-1 home victory over the Toronto Maple Leafs.

headline.main: One Rookie Goalie Outshines Another as the Jets Win
